A massive crystalline polyhedron structure floating in a deep violet void, its facets reflecting and refracting streams of molten gold and electric blue energy that flow through its transparent core. The structure appears to be mid-transformation, with geometric shards breaking away from one side while simultaneously assembling into a more refined, compact form on the other. Tiny glowing particles trail behind the transforming segments like digital stardust. The scene has a cyberpunk aesthetic with neon accent lighting, holographic grid lines barely visible in the background, and a sense of powerful computational processes made tangible. The polyhedron casts complex caustic light patterns into the surrounding darkness, suggesting both raw processing power and elegant optimization happening simultaneously.
